INSERT INTO `field_revision_field_slide_text` VALUES ('field_collection_item','field_slide',0,1,1,'und',0,'Tempt Large Format professionals collaborate with clients to create and produce innovative, eye-popping visuals and retail environments that grab attention, drive traffic and promote the brand.',NULL),('field_collection_item','field_slide',0,3,3,'und',0,'Tempt Large Format professionals collaborate with clients to create and produce innovative, eye-popping visuals and retail environments that grab attention, drive traffic and promote the brand.',NULL),('field_collection_item','field_slide',0,4,4,'und',0,'Tempt Large Format professionals collaborate with clients to create and produce innovative, eye-popping visuals and retail environments that grab attention, drive traffic and promote the brand.',NULL),('field_collection_item','field_slide',0,5,5,'und',0,'<h1>Retail</h1>Create innovative environmental graphics and window displays that drive traffic. From concept to completion including design consultation, cost effective production and solutions<br> kit, pack, delivered and up in the store fast!	',NULL),('field_collection_item','field_slide',0,6,6,'und',0,'<h1>Financial</h1>While there are many transactions in the world, one thing that is not for sale is customer loyalty.<br> Use direct mail, permanent in-store displays to create the right environment and <br>promotional materials to promote the brand and connect with customers.',NULL),('field_collection_item','field_slide',0,7,7,'und',0,'<h1>Sports</h1>Create excitement, foster rivalries or motivate the amateur athlete with single or multi-dimensional visuals that stand out to move the product and promote the brand.	',NULL),('field_collection_item','field_slide',0,8,8,'und',0,'<h1>Automotive</h1>Create a showroom that becomes a backdrop for the vehicle and the brand. Wrap cars, shuttle vans, and buses to create mobile billboards. From vehicle wraps and showroom graphics to direct mail and bounce back coupons, Vertis can help you reach your target audience and capture their attention.',NULL),('field_collection_item','field_slide',0,9,9,'und',0,'<h1>Restaurant</h1>Quick serve or specialty sit down: create the backdrop and set the stage. Our professional team can recommend solutions to encompass just right atmosphere, table top cards, promotional mailings, floor/window graphics and clings, menu boards, and drive thru promotions.',NULL),('field_collection_item','field_slide',0,10,10,'und',0,'<h1>Tradeshow & Events</h1>Everything must be perfect and it’s always down to the wire! We get it. So don’t worry, we will ask all the right questions, get the prints delivered, handle the install, get the collateral shipped correctly and double check the address. That’s what we do to create the environment to help you sell!',NULL),('field_collection_item','field_slide',0,11,11,'und',0,'<h1>Grocery</h1>Craft exciting endcap displays that target the in-­and-­out shoppers with bold colors and large text. Or engage the opportunistic consumer who is browsing with graphics about farming techniques<br> recipe ideas, nutritional information, and value statements.',NULL),('field_collection_item','field_slide',0,12,12,'und',0,'<h1>Banners</h1>Banners are a classic graphic format that can be used indoors and outdoors to draw attention<br> and drive traffic. They can be produced single- or double-sided for events, promotions,<br>  directional signage, or to set the tone for a retail environment. ',NULL),('field_collection_item','field_slide',0,13,13,'und',0,'<h1>Window Graphics</h1>Stop traffic with decals and clings that can adhere directly on a glass surface. Create full color visuals for high impact messaging or print on clear to create artist impressions and lend <br>depth and dimension to your window or cashwrap display.',NULL),('field_collection_item','field_slide',0,14,14,'und',0,'<h1>Magnets</h1>Vertis’ magnetic and steel paper stock solutions allow quick updates to existing advertisements w